      "text": "Planner To Pulses\nIn a step/dir system, the controller converts\ntrajectory segments into timed step pulses and\ndirection states.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 15.0,
      "containerId": "node-b51f2f64c86d",
      "originalText": "Planner To Pulses\nIn a step/dir system, the controller converts trajectory segments into timed step pulses and direction states.",
