      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 17.5,
      "containerId": "node-e82c9d2f6e0a",
      "originalText": "Feedback Path\nFeedback closes the gap between commanded motion and actual motion at the drive, controller, or measurement layer.",
