      "text": "Z Axis Channel\nThe Z motor output commands tool height and needs\nconservative acceleration because crashes and gravity\neffects are concentrated here.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 15.0,
      "containerId": "node-1c3c1c648f9d",
      "originalText": "Z Axis Channel\nThe Z motor output commands tool height and needs conservative acceleration because crashes and gravity effects are concentrated here.",
