      "text": "Fault Boundary\nDrives detect overcurrent, overvoltage, undervoltage,\novertemperature, encoder faults, following error, and\nstall conditions before damage grows.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 15.0,
      "containerId": "node-c0decbd8badd",
      "originalText": "Fault Boundary\nDrives detect overcurrent, overvoltage, undervoltage, overtemperature, encoder faults, following error, and stall conditions before damage grows.",
