      "text": "Microstepping\nMicrostepping shapes sine-like phase currents to\nreduce vibration and resonance, but it does not create\nfull-step torque at every microstep.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 15.0,
      "containerId": "node-1a809377e651",
