      "text": "Back EMF\nAs speed rises, the motor generates voltage opposing\nthe drive, reducing available current and torque\nmargin.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 15.0,
      "containerId": "node-085e2a444206",
      "originalText": "Back EMF\nAs speed rises, the motor generates voltage opposing the drive, reducing available current and torque margin.",
