      "text": "Star Vs Plane\nSmall machines often use star-like returns, while\nindustrial cabinets use bonded metal backplanes and\nshort low-impedance connections.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 15.0,
      "containerId": "node-cd5b3a266df2",
