      "text": "Jitter Budget\nTiming jitter becomes path error, velocity noise, or\nsurface finish error when axes do not update evenly.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 15.0,
      "containerId": "node-a83f90f1e5b1",
      "originalText": "Jitter Budget\nTiming jitter becomes path error, velocity noise, or surface finish error when axes do not update evenly.",
