      "text": "Servo Conversion\nA servo upgrade changes motor sizing, inertia\nmatching, tuning, braking, fault handling, and often\nmechanical expectations.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 15.0,
      "containerId": "node-1b129d14720e",
      "originalText": "Servo Conversion\nA servo upgrade changes motor sizing, inertia matching, tuning, braking, fault handling, and often mechanical expectations.",
